Package: incul
Version: 2.0.1
Architecture: all
Maintainer: Muna Bedan <munabedan@gmail.com>
Description: Lightweight container-based desktop compartmentalization.
  Incul uses Incus and Xpra under the hood to let you run separate,
  isolated environments for everyday tasks without the overhead of full 
  virtual machines. You can keep different applications, projects, or 
  libraries neatly compartmentalized, making it easy to organize your 
  desktop activities.
Depends: python3, python3-netifaces, python3-cups, python3-opencv, python3-pip , python3-gi-cairo, xfce4-notifyd, incus, yq, openssh-client
